      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BETTORCHECKHEROUT (3) has shown plenty of promise in winning her two starts at this circuit and distance so far, coming from this barrier both times. Worked when racing three wide in the middle stages last start before setting outside the leader and still proving too strong by more than 6m. Can deliver again. PASSION AND PAIN (5) has more than 6m to make up on BETTORCHECKHEROUT through her debut second but she draws closer to the pegs and should be better for the experience. There was plenty to like about the debut performance of MICKS CRUZA (8) when he led from a similar barrier before digging deep to score at this circuit and distance. With natural improvement likely he could go on with it. UNJUST ENRICHMENT (10) may need a touch of luck from the back row but did a good job to miss narrowly on debut.",
